headline: Should ABN AMRO’s Gen Z Card Partnership Shape the Investment Narrative for Visa (V)?
summary: In September 2025, ABN AMRO announced a partnership with Visa and Pismo to power BUUT's new debit card, designed specifically for Gen Z consumers and built using Pismo's cloud-native platform in just 10 weeks. This collaboration reflects Visa's expanding influence in enabling banks to rapidly develop digital-first financial products and signals the growing adoption of API-based, cloud-native infrastructures to better meet evolving consumer preferences.
